                  Conference      Market Dynamics in the Arab Gulf and Other Emerging Economies                  Invitation Only                                    Date                   Thursday, April 28, 2011                                                             Time           9:00am - 5:00pm                                                     Location           19 Washington Square North Events Space                     View map                                          Related Links                              Agenda                                                                     This conference addresses the long-term growth prospects in the UAE and the region with a focus on labor and financial markets. Theoretical and empirical analyses will be presented to stimulate discussions on future macroeconomic research for the region.
